__notoc__ bartholomew cubbins , a page , is the hero of two children 's story books by dr. seuss : the 500 hats of bartholomew cubbins ( 1938 ) and bartholomew and the oobleck ( 1949 ) .

children 's lit : 2 of his many books are " the foot book " & " the 500 hats of bartholomew cubbins "

